<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="87">It is a privilege to name this new species after Canadian astronaut Col. Chris Hadfield for his many achievements as a pilot, astronaut, author, lecturer, and science educator.</paragraph>
